Commented on #7 ISSUE when same word exists in both movie names from same YEAR

The addon receives the IMDb ID and uses it to get a name and year. it then searches Google Drive for files containing both the name and year. we can only search Google Drive with simple text search. if a file contains both the correct name and the correct year, it will inevitably meet the search criteria. This is an edge case that I can't fix

div.div: High-school beauty Umaru seems like the perfect teen wunderkind, but she's hiding a shocking double life. As soon as she gets home, she becomes a junk-food-inhaling, soda-guzzling, video-game-addicted slob. The only one who sees this unsavory side of Umaru is her beleaguered older brother Taihei, who does his best to keep up with his work while trying to get his little sister to behave like a decent member of society. As she makes new friends and gets into a number of wacky situations, Umaru will continue to fight for her right to stay up all night binging potato chips and anime. (Source: Anime News Network)
Episodes included in the manga's seventh and tenth volume.

Jirou, a third-year in high school, is forced to live with a gyaru named Akari under a course called the "Couple Practical". In order to be paired with their own romantic interests, they're going to act as a married couple...!? <i>Note: Nominated for the Tsugimanga 2020 Award in the Manga Category.<i>
Wo Neng Fu Zhi Tian Fu

Ye Tian gained the power to copy others' talents. In order to protect his sister, he struggled to survive in the apocalyptic era of the invasion of exotic beasts. In order to become stronger, he began to explore the unknown world and gradually uncovered the secrets of the invasion of different dimensions...
(Source: MangaToon)

Helmut was only a baby when he was left in the Forest of Pahe, an evil place full of beasts where sinners are banished for eternity. Luckily, one magical beast and an exiled swordsman take pity on him and raise him as their own. But with a dark seed growing inside him, Helmut decides to take up the sword to prevent the seed from turning him evil. As Helmut grows stronger, he seeks out the family that abandoned him, but will Helmut end up following his human heart or his beastly instincts?
(Source: Tapas)
Otonari no Tenshi-sama ni Itsunomanika Dame Ningen ni Sareteita Ken

Amane Fujimiya lives alone in a messy apartment—right next door to Mahiru Shiina, a veritable "angel" who's the smartest, prettiest girl at school. When a chance encounter on a rainy day draws them together, Mahiru finds herself spending more and more time helping Amane get his life in order. And though they both insist they have no intention of dating the other, slowly but surely, something more than friendship begins to blossom.
(Source: Square Enix)
Doukyonin ga Konoyo no Mon Janai
Comedy, Ecchi, Horror, Romance, Slice of Life, Supernatural

The young man's new apartment is haunted, but as it turns out, even the dead have their own personal shortcomings... issues of the flesh included.
For the dead have lingering desires and are more susceptible to the world of the living than what one may think. There's anger, there's hate, there's curiosity... and there's love too.
Here he finds a ghastly girl who observes him quietly, certainly desiring something...
